    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements given medium model influence. RH < 1.0 at all 5 operating points satisfies the predicate device comparison acceptance criterion. CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device 510(k) submission. Note: the ContextOfUse does not specify an applicability constraint or operating envelope, leaving the boundary of valid model use implicitly defined only by the validation operating points.",
